abstract: BALTIMORE, Jan. 19 (AP) Tom Meschery led the San  Francisco Warriors to a 123102 victory over the New York Knicks tonight in the first game of a National Basketball Association double-header.
headline_main: NEW YORK PLAYER KNOCKS DOWN FOE; Meschery Scores 28 Points for Warriors Bullets Top Royals in 2d Game
